{"tid":1479081,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好信任何有鬼既post 慎防\"白色恐怖\"","createTime":"2019-08-16T18:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T19:30:32.000Z","uid":220853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57e6428ffa4b70c8639a4720bc003e5f00b2062c","tid":1479081,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:15:33.000Z","msg":"只要發現任何話將會有鬼 / 捉鬼 post<br />\n必須起底 查明<br />\n佢地目的只係散佈白色恐怖<br />\n令和理非會怕左去和平遊行/集會<br />\n如果你連和平遊行都唔去 你就係一隻港豬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共一直用恐懼統治平民<br />\n如果你被恐懼屈服<br />\n你一世都只能低頭</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除了恐懼本身以外，沒有任何可以恐懼的事</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n第二十七條 <br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。"},{"pid":"f9962122ac548bec9a946c04e15c88aaf0ad11e2","tid":1479081,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:16:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"121595ed3e8c6b960b247601da772031d93edac5","tid":1479081,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:16:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"489dfaf7418e164bbda6510ec4f8fa90242b70a2","tid":1479081,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:21:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 2點 維園見<br />\n大家一定要出！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a14Krun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa14Krun.jpg&h=f12c1c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkxLVot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkxLVot.jpg&h=9b3f8527&s={SIZE}\" /><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xg1EfoE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXg1EfoE.jpg&h=24a18478&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vynXB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i